      "text": "Letter to Director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "June 8, 1954",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "which [REDACTED] had with a crew of assumed space explorers under",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "the supervision of a ravishing woman commandant in the Nevada desert.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "The article also reflects that [REDACTED] allegedly was aboard",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "flying saucers on eleven occasions. At the bottom of the first page",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "of issue number 15 there appeared in what Mr. [REDACTED] stated was the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "handwriting of [REDACTED] the statement \"This is a true story, a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "factual experience -- [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "The above mentioned article in \"Valor\" also reflected that [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] 55 years of age and that his residence address is [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Redondo Beach, California.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] also had with him a letter addressed to [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "from [REDACTED] of the Saucers Research Foundation, which letter re-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "flected that that organization was holding a three-day convention June 4,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "5 and 6, 1954 at the Carthay Circle Theatre in Los Angeles, California,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "and that it had invited [REDACTED] to this convention to say a few",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "words concerning his experience. [REDACTED] was identified in this letter as",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "business manager of [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Hollywood 46, California.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] reiterated that he felt [REDACTED] story, if true,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "should be given wide publicity, but that if the story was false, then he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "should be prosecuted for fraud. He stated that he first took his in-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "formation to the Air Force in the person of Lieutenant Colonel [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "[REDACTED] of Wright-Patterson Air Force Base, Ohio, whom [REDACTED] visited",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "personally at [REDACTED] home in Fairborn, Ohio, on Sunday, 6-6-54.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "[REDACTED] indicated that he asked Colonel [REDACTED] if there were such things",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "as flying saucers and if [REDACTED] story could be true, and he said",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[REDACTED] denied that there was such a thing as a flying saucer and indicated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "to him that DONALD E. KEHOE, the author of \"Flying Saucers in Outer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Space\" was a fraud and that information is available in Washington that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "KEHOE is a fraud. He said he was advised, however, by [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "that the Air Force could take no action with respect to [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "[REDACTED] continued that it was his intention to aid in the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "promotion of a meeting for [REDACTED] in Cincinnati. He advised that the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "original meeting scheduled for June 11 had been cancelled, and that he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "felt this meeting had such important information for the people as a whole",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
